name: The Law Office of Matthew L. Byrne
tag_list: criminal-defense, attoney, lawyer, jail-release, bail-bonds, dwi, expungement, expunction, austin-texas
overview:
Matt Byrne is a solo criminal defense lawyer providing jail release and zealous repesentation in downtown Austin.

Emergency Travis County jail release calls are welcome 24 hours, and all messages are promptly returned. If your friend or loved one has been arrested in the Austin area, call to discuss how to obtain a personal recognizance bond and get them out of jail quickly.

Call to schedule an appointment if you are facing misdemeanor or felony allegations, including DWI, DUI, drug crimes, assault, and theft.

If you have a criminal record which includes charges that were dismissed or for which you completed deferred adjudication or a pre-trial diversion program, call to discuss whether you may be eligible for criminal record expungement or an order of non-disclosure.

All initial consultations are free, confidential, and without obligation.
